    <textTemplates>
        <name>txt_EmailBody</name>
        <isViewedAsPlainText>false</isViewedAsPlainText>
        <text>&lt;p&gt;Dear {!Get_Account.FirstName} {!Get_Account.LastName},&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We hope you are doing well. We are excited to provide you with the key to access our Patient Success Portal, where you can update your demographic data within our system. Your prompt response is appreciated, as it ensures we have the most accurate and up-to-date information to serve you better.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Please use the following link to navigate to the Patient Success Portal:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://patient.10xhealthsystem.com/s/patientupdate&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;https://patient.10xhealthsystem.com/s/patientupdate&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Once on the portal, simply enter the key provided below in the designated text box to log in and update your information:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Key: {!Get_Account.Customer_Digital_Key__c}&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Keeping your key safe and confidential is crucial, as it serves as your unique identifier within our system, ensuring the security of your data.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you have any questions or need assistance during the update process, our support team is ready to help. Feel free to contact them at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:support@10xhealthsystem.com&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;support@10xhealthsystem.com&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Best regards,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;{!$User.FirstName} {!$User.LastName}&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Customer Support Team&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;10&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(209, 36, 42);&quot;&gt;x&lt;/span&gt; Health System&lt;/p&gt;</text>
    </textTemplates>
